Remarkable renovations have transformed this pool home

This immaculately renovated pool home, with four bedrooms, three baths and a three-car garage, is situated on a beautifully landscaped beachside corner lot. A newly installed paver walkway leads into the sun-drenched open floor plan, offering custom appointments that are sure to impress the most discriminating buyer. This exquisite property features a new roof, impact-resistant windows and doors, insulated impact-resistant garage doors, HVAC, plumbing and updated electrical. The designer kitchen offers all-wood, soft-close cabinets, granite and quartz countertops, cafe (wi-fi compatible) appliances, a stainless-steel farmhouse sink and ample storage. Luxury vinyl-plank flooring adorns the main living spaces, and each bathroom features custom porcelain tile/marble that provides a timeless design. The stunning owner’s suite features a spa-like bath and a private entrance to the backyard, which holds the paver-surrounded pool, new vinyl fencing, new sod, lush native landscaping and plenty of space for entertaining.
ADDRESS: 17 W. Sovereign Lane, Ormond Beach
CONTACT: Chrissy Royce, Adams, Cameron & Co. Realtors, 386-451-8351
